OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FScattered
OL,6,Fevening showers will soon clear
OL,7,Feastwards leaving dry conditions and
OL,8,Fclear spells for a time overnight.
OL,9,FBecoming cloudy by morning with patchy
OL,10,Flight rain arriving.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA mostly cloudy day with
OL,13,Fsome patchy light rain, mainly in the
OL,14,Fafternoon along Deeside. Drier across
OL,15,FMoray and north Aberdeenshire with a
OL,16,Flittle brightness.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
